{"tid":1530102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"合法進入機場客運大樓","createTime":"2019-09-02T01:08:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T04:17:14.000Z","uid":97997,"like":115,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"2726268afb122bd7c8fdfc982ac5b2d3707f38c8","tid":1530102,"uid":97997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T01:08:58.000Z","msg":"作為一個飛機迷，去T2個垃圾觀景台睇飛機係再正常不過嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係AA竟然禁止市民進入客運大樓，仲要申請禁制令，意圖令人以為進入機場客運大樓食飯睇戲會違反禁制令<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n作為奉公守法市民，一定唔會硬闖客運大樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就嘗試改pdf舊機票內容，但係原來好多航空公司都有用特殊字體，改日期會match唔到字體<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我竟然冇發覺到，原來forward email俾自己嘅時候，edit封email就可以改日期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家可以將舊機票日期改做入客運大樓辦事嘅日子，帶埋passport就可以入機場睇飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n反正機場保安根本唔會打電話去航空公司問有冇呢個乘客，否則AA會自行堵塞機場<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kuJp7SU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkuJp7SU.jpg&h=c9c0dbb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屌你唔好求其啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YCEEcmF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYCEEcmF.jpg&h=ab751ac7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n國泰機票一樣得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c473b8f92d8764f424078e161fc534222eb6a789","tid":1530102,"uid":73565,"like":74,"dislike":8,"score":66,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T01:10:19.000Z","msg":"虛假文書 入硬<br />\n入到一個半個 後面果啲死哂"},{"pid":"1b9a9e36f54acf25528e04e01a30c173cafcf148","tid":1530102,"uid":49055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T01:10:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0a14b88f7f44bc5c05671678526f120530e167c6","tid":1530102,"uid":75664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T01:10:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b83f1b52fa77fddde84eb9eee173d1eea1ebb6d1","tid":1530102,"uid":49055,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"c473b8f92d8764f424078e161fc534222eb6a789","tid":1530102,"uid":73565,"like":74,"dislike":8,"score":66,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T01:10:19.000Z","msg":"虛假文書 入硬<br />\n入到一個半個 後面果啲死哂"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T01:11:14.000Z","msg":"咁狗鐵算唔算？"},{"pid":"0fc5dee403e25861b17d8e7d5d49fd3531128d00","tid":1530102,"uid":219244,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T01:11:38.000Z","msg":"如果係咁要帶埋個篋去扮遊客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6e3b226913a0d563cdc857715f404f837aec096","tid":1530102,"uid":149575,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b83f1b52fa77fddde84eb9eee173d1eea1ebb6d1","tid":1530102,"uid":49055,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"c473b8f92d8764f424078e161fc534222eb6a789","tid":1530102,"uid":73565,"like":74,"dislike":8,"score":66,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T01:10:19.000Z","msg":"虛假文書 入硬<br />\n入到一個半個 後面果啲死哂"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T01:11:14.000Z","msg":"咁狗鐵算唔算？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T01:12:54.000Z","msg":"佢企黨果邊點都無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c3b8993e102bff78d0793ed363b848dd9d29ae6","tid":1530102,"uid":73381,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"c473b8f92d8764f424078e161fc534222eb6a789","tid":1530102,"uid":73565,"like":74,"dislike":8,"score":66,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T01:10:19.000Z","msg":"虛假文書 入硬<br />\n入到一個半個 後面果啲死哂"},"citedBy":1,"replyTim